		function updatePrice(number,price,id,stock,sale, oldprice,active, discountmode) {
			if (sale) {
                jQuery('#price--holder, #price--holder--bottom').html('' +
                    '<div class="price-holder wide price-special relative flex flex-wrap margin-right-xs margin-bottom-xs">' +
                        '<span class="price price-old pull-left">' +
                            '<span class="currency">&euro;</span>' +
                            '<span class="cost_inclusive oldprice"> '+oldprice+'</span>' +
                        '</span>' +
                        '<span class="price price-current pull-left">' +
                            '<span class="currency">&euro;</span>' +
                            '<span class="cost_inclusive newprice"> '+price+'</span>' +
                        '</span>' +
                        // '<span class="badge tag">Sale!</span>' + disabled due to new discount layout
                    '</div>');
			} else {
                jQuery('#price--holder, #price--holder--bottom').html('' +
                '<div class="price-holder price-normal pull-left margin-right-xs margin-bottom-xs">' +
                    '<span class="price price-current pull-left">' +
                        '<span class="currency">&euro;</span>' +
                        '<span class="cost_inclusive newprice"> '+price+'</span>' +
                   ' </span>' +
                '</div>');
			}

			if (discountmode) {
                jQuery.post(
                    '?layout=discount-badge&tmpl=component',
                    {
                        'combo_id': id
                    },
                    function (data) {
                        if (data.badge) {
                            jQuery('#discount-badges').show().html(data.badge);
                        } else {
                            jQuery('#discount-badges').html('').hide();
                        }
                        if (data.box) {
                            jQuery('#discount-boxes').show().html(data.box);
                        } else {
                            jQuery('#discount-boxes').html('').hide();
                        }
                    },"json"
                );
            } else {
                jQuery('#discount-badges').html('').hide();
                jQuery('#discount-boxes').html('').hide();
            }

			if (stock > 0 && active) {
                jQuery('#final--product-holder').removeClass('disabled');
                jQuery('#primary-btn').removeClass('btn-inactive').attr('onclick','addToCart();return false;').removeAttr('disabled');
                jQuery('#primary-btn--bottom').removeClass('btn-inactive').attr('onclick','addToCart();return false;').removeAttr('disabled');
                jQuery('#product-qty--select').attr('onchange','changeQuantityProduct(this.value);return false;').removeAttr('disabled');
                jQuery('#product-qty--select--bottom').attr('onchange','changeQuantityProduct(this.value);return false;').removeAttr('disabled');
                if (stock >= 10) {
                    jQuery('span.availability').addClass('in-stock').removeClass('out-of-stock').find('span').text('Beschikbaar');
                    jQuery('#final--product-holder .col-66 .availability').addClass('in-stock').removeClass('out-of-stock').find('span').text('Beschikbaar');

                } else {
                    jQuery('span.availability').addClass('in-stock').removeClass('out-of-stock').find('span').text('Nog maar '+ stock + ' op voorraad');
                    jQuery('#final--product-holder .col-66 .availability').addClass('in-stock').removeClass('out-of-stock').find('span').text('Nog maar '+ stock + ' op voorraad');
                }
                var options = '';
                for(var i=1;i<=(stock > 10 ? 10 : stock);i++) {
                    options += '<option value="'+i+'">'+i+'</option>';
                }
                jQuery('#product-qty--select').html(options);
                jQuery('#product-qty--select--bottom').html(options);
			} else {
                jQuery('#final--product-holder').addClass('disabled');
				jQuery('span.availability').addClass('out-of-stock').removeClass('in-stock').find('span').text('Beschikbaar');
				jQuery('#final--product-holder .col-66 .availability').addClass('out-of-stock').removeClass('in-stock').find('span').text('Beschikbaar');
                jQuery('#primary-btn').addClass('btn-inactive').attr('onclick','return false;').attr('disabled','disabled');
                jQuery('#primary-btn--bottom').addClass('btn-inactive').attr('onclick','return false;').attr('disabled','disabled');
                jQuery('#product-qty--select').attr('onchange','return false;').attr('disabled','disabled');
                jQuery('#product-qty--select--bottom').attr('onchange','return false;').attr('disabled','disabled');
			}

            jQuery('.product-variant--images-thumbs--images ul li').each(function(){
                jQuery(this).find('a').removeClass('active');
            });

            jQuery('#product-thumb-' + id).addClass('active');
            jQuery('.product--selectbox > span').each(function(){
                jQuery(this).removeClass('active');
            });
            jQuery('.product--selectbox #combination-' + id).addClass('active');

            updateStock();
            getProduct(id, price);
		}

		function getProduct(id, price) {
			var img = jQuery('#combination-' + id + ' img').attr('src');
			var h3 = jQuery('#combination-' + id + ' span.h3').html();
			var finalProduct = jQuery('#final--product-holder');
			var finalProductImg = finalProduct.find('.col-20');
            var finalProductContent = finalProduct.find('.col-80');
            var productStickyHeader = jQuery('.product-sticky-header');

            if(productStickyHeader.length&&$(window).width()>=768) {
                productStickyHeader.find('img').attr("src", img);
                productStickyHeader.find('h3').html('Zuiver hoekbank Fiep<span class="divider">-</span><span>' + h3 + '</span>');
                productStickyHeader.find('.product-price').html('&euro; ' + price);

                    jQuery("#primary-btn").click();
                    return false;
                });

			jQuery('.product--selectbox--variant--selected').html(

				'<span class="h3">Zuiver hoekbank Fiep<span class="divider">-</span><span>'+ h3 +'</span></span>' +
				'<span class="product--selectbox--variant--price no-wrap">&euro; '+price+'</span>');

            finalProductContent.find('.col-33').find('p').html(h3);
			var decodedThmbString = atob(jQuery('#thmbsarr').val());
			var thmbsobj = jQuery.parseJSON(decodedThmbString);
			if (thmbsobj[id]) {
                if (thmbsobj[id][480]) {
                    finalProductImg.html('<img src="'+thmbsobj[id][480]['url']+'" class="wide" />');
                } else {
                    var decodedImgString = atob(jQuery('#imgsarr').val());
                    var imgsobj = jQuery.parseJSON(decodedImgString);
                    if (imgsobj[id]) {
                        finalProductImg.html('<img src="' + imgsobj[id] + '" class="wide" />');
                    } else {
                        finalProductImg.html('<img src="/templates/loods5/images/misc/broken-image.png" class="wide" />');
                    }
                }
            } else {
                finalProductImg.html('<img src="/templates/loods5/images/misc/broken-image.png" class="wide" />');
            }

            var decodedAttrsString = atob(jQuery('#c_attribs').val());
            var attrs = jQuery.parseJSON(decodedAttrsString);

            jQuery('#combo--specs .dyn--specs').remove();

                if (attrs[id]) {

                        jQuery('#combo--specs').append('' +
                            '<li class="product-page-specs--spec dyn--specs">\n' +
                            '    <span class="product-page-specs--spec--label">\n' +

                            val.join(", ") + '\n' +
                            '    </span>\n' +
                            '</li>');
                    });
                }
            }

            var decodedAttribsExtraString = atob(jQuery('#c_attribs_extra').val());
            var attribs_extra = jQuery.parseJSON(decodedAttribsExtraString);
            if (attribs_extra) {
                if (attribs_extra[id]) {
                    jQuery.map(attribs_extra[id], function (val, i) {
                        // console.log(val);
                        jQuery('#combo--specs').append('' +
                            '<li class="product-page-specs--spec dyn--specs">\n' +
                            '    <span class="product-page-specs--spec--label">\n' +
                            i + '\n' +
                            '    </span>\n' +
                            '    <span class="product-page-specs--spec--value">\n' +
                            val + '\n' +
                            '    </span>\n' +
                            '</li>');
                    });
                }
            }

            var decodedDimensionsString = atob(jQuery('#c_dimensions').val());
            var dimensions = jQuery.parseJSON(decodedDimensionsString);
            if (dimensions) {
                if (dimensions[id]) {
                    jQuery('#combo--dimensions--holder').show();
                    jQuery('#combo--dimensions .dyn--specs').remove();
                    jQuery.map(dimensions[id], function (val, i) {
                        // console.log(val);
                        jQuery('#combo--dimensions').append('' +
                            '<li class="product-page-specs--spec dyn--specs">\n' +
                            '    <span class="product-page-specs--spec--label">\n' +
                            i + '\n' +
                            '    </span>\n' +
                            '    <span class="product-page-specs--spec--value">\n' +
                            val + '\n' +
                            '    </span>\n' +
                            '</li>');
                    });
                } else {
                    jQuery('#combo--dimensions--holder').hide();
                }
            } else {
                jQuery('#combo--dimensions--holder').hide();
            }

            // var thumbslider = jQuery('#product-images-thumbs-slider');
            // var largeslider = jQuery('#product-images-slider');
            if (totalcount > 3) {
                thumbslider.slick('slickUnfilter').slick(
                    'slickFilter', '.product-thumb--combo-' + id + ', .product-thumb--image').slick(
                    'slickGoTo', 0
                ).slick(

            }

            largeslider.slick(
                'slickFilter', '.product-thumb--combo-' + id + ', .product-thumb--image');
            largeslider.slick(
                'slickGoTo', 0
            );
            largeslider.slick(
                'refresh'
            );
            //Keep Campaign Tags
            var combination_id = '13587';
            var url = '/product/5364/zuiver-hoekbank-fiep/' + id;

            if (window.location.search) {
                url += window.location.search
            }

            if (window.location.hash) {
                url += window.location.hash
            }

            window.history.replaceState(combination_id, 'title', url);

        function updateStock() {
            var store = jQuery('#store-stock option:selected').val();
            var vars = jQuery('.product--selectbox--variant.active').attr('id');
            var comboid = vars.split('combination-')[1];
            var decodedString = atob(jQuery('#jsstk').val());
            var obj = jQuery.parseJSON(decodedString);

            if (store) {
                jQuery('.store-result').show();
                if (obj[comboid][store] > 0) {
                    if (obj[comboid][store] >= 10) {
                        jQuery('.store-result .store-result-stock').addClass('in-stock').removeClass('out-of-stock').text('Beschikbaar');
                    } else {
                        jQuery('.store-result .store-result-stock').addClass('in-stock').removeClass('out-of-stock').text('Nog maar '+ obj[comboid][store] + ' beschikbaar');
                    }
                } else {
                    jQuery('.store-result .store-result-stock').addClass('out-of-stock').removeClass('in-stock').text('Niet op voorraad');
                }
            } else {
                jQuery('.store-result').hide();
            }
        }

        function addToWishlist() {
            var vars = jQuery('.product--selectbox--variant.active').attr('id');
            var combination = vars.split('combination-')[1];
            jQuery.post(
                "/api/jquery.functions.php",
                {
                    "function": 'addToWishlist',
                    "combination": combination
                },
                function (data) {
                    if (data.result === 'success') {
                        var modalhref = '/components/com_static/views/checkout/tmpl/cart--modal--wishlist.php';
                        var modalclass = '.'+modalhref.split('/').pop().slice(0, -4); // -4 = .php
                        jQuery.ajax({
                            url: modalhref,
                            success: function (data) {
                                jQuery("body").append(data).addClass('modal--is-open');
                                jQuery(modalclass).fadeIn(200);
                            },
                            dataType: 'html'
                        });
                    }
                },
                "json"
            );
        }

        function changeQuantityProduct(qty) {
            if(qty === 'meer') {
                jQuery('#product-qty--select').hide();
                jQuery('#product-qty--select--bottom').hide();
                jQuery('#product-qty--input').show();
            } else if(qty > 10) {
                jQuery('#product-qty--select').hide();
                jQuery('#product-qty--select--bottom').hide();
            } else {
                jQuery('#product-qty--input').hide();
                jQuery('#product-qty--select option[value="'+qty+'"]').attr('selected','selected');
                jQuery('#product-qty--select--bottom option[value="'+qty+'"]').attr('selected','selected');
            }
        }
